iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpDocSpecification, Spuri, SpUserNotice

    public class SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements iaik.asn1.ASN1Type
    This class is used to further qualify a SignaturePolicyIdentifier. The ASN.1 structure is as following: SigPolicyQualifierInfo ::= SEQUENCE { sigPolicyQualifierId SigPolicyQualifierId, sigQualifier ANY DEFINED BY sigPolicyQualifierId } SigPolicyQualifierId ::= OBJECT IDENTIFIER
